？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T15:52:00.000Z","msg":"仲用緊拐杖，傷口仲痛，隻腳未消哂腫，如果返文職勉強都仲可以"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:55:49.000Z","msg":"要吉住拐杖返工，但又請唔到咁長假 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:59:39.000Z","msg":"No pay 都要架la,因為會整到傷口，痛又辛苦，點迫巴士地鐵<br />\n到時會有個腳套俾你戴限制膝關節幅度，唔俾你屈曲咁多，唔通坐巴士地鐵伸直隻腳咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e233b4909cad280d0e7ef56dcae59797811091e6","tid":967252,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T08:00:58.000Z","msg":"做過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你斷左唔做以後都係拗拗下<br />\n4星期只係行到, 落樓梯要3個月"},{"pid":"cfe19974217492b72e1b394ce3981a7e11674bbe","tid":967252,"uid":195588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T08:03:45.000Z","msg":"做完第二日醫生黎到病床<br />\n話變個魔術俾我睇<br />\n即刻係我大脾抽條好長既膠管出黎<br />\n嚇撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed35cc4a7048b5abc82011a4e321e238f0538e45","tid":967252,"uid":102138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T08:04:18.000Z","msg":"唉屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係半年傷殘走唔甩<br />\n做之前洗唔洗練定啲四頭肌先?"},{"pid":"b3084d57f882b3c336b97392b980eb913a80e899","tid":967252,"uid":102138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cfe19974217492b72e1b394ce3981a7e11674bbe","tid":967252,"uid":195588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T08:03:45.000Z","msg":"做完第二日醫生黎到病床<br />\n話變個魔術俾我睇<br />\n即刻係我大脾抽條好長既膠管出黎<br />\n嚇撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T08:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔痛架咩?"},{"pid":"1bd7e755880b5670e62f63e2e22f2aa7a1e576dd","tid":967252,"uid":166944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T10:01:41.000Z","msg":"On99<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma